      "para_id": "Q001526.1",
      "line_range": "1",
      "translation": "(back 1) To Ninegala , her lady , ... ( this object ) for the well-being of Gudea , ruler of Lagaš ."
    },
    {
      "para_id": "Q001526.8",
      "line_range": "8",
      "translation": "(base 1') She fashioned ( her statue ) and brought it before her in the temple . The name of this statue is \" Ninegala ( is ) my lady !\"."
    }
  ],
